{"type": "article", "id": 36895, "title": "全球最大眼镜和镜片公司合并，以及，日本星巴克与 BEAMS 推了配饰 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-01-17T02:45:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 15798, "name": "NEIGHBORHOOD"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 873, "name": "星巴克"}, {"id": 1099, "name": "资生堂"}, {"id": 32759, "name": "Happy Socks"}, {"id": 5146, "name": "周杰伦"}, {"id": 18765, "name": "藤原浩"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170117102631C0fmPOqJup2F3jdg.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/business/palamons-foothold-in-happy-socks-hh5csfs2c\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>瑞典著名的袜子品牌 Happy Socks，被收购大部分股份</b></a> | 私募股权公司 Palamon Capital Partners，斥资约 6740 万英镑，收购了 Happy Socks 大部分股份。后者是一家创业于 2008 年的公司，以出售很活泼的袜子著称，目前已在 90 多个国家和地区开设了专柜。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/shiseido-names-president-of-china-operations-10751693/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>资生堂任命新的中国区代表</b></a> | 昨日，资生堂宣布原资生堂（中国）投资有限公司总经理藤原宪太郎正式升任资生堂中国总代表一职。上任之后，藤原宪太郎将负责集团全球组织架构的改组，设立中国地区总部。</p><p><b><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/luxxotica-to-merge-with-essilor-creating-46-billion-euro-eyewear-giant/\" rel=\"nofollow\">全球最大的眼镜公司和镜片公司合并</a></b> | 意大利眼镜制造商 Luxottica 与法国镜片制造商 Essilor 在周一达成合并协议。合并后的新公司名为 EssilorLuxottica，市值达到  490 亿美元。Luxottica 的创始人 Leonardo Del Vecchio 将成为合并后公司最大的单一股东，持股约 30％ ，他还将出任新公司的首席执行官。&nbsp;<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/starbucks-x-beamsstarbucks-touch-the-drip\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本星巴克与 BEAMS 百货联手推出了 Starbucks Touch the Drip 挂饰</a>，还挺好看的。这款挂饰的正面印有星巴克的人鱼图案，底部则是 </font>Designed by BEAMS 字样，共有 5 个配色，售价为税后 4240 日元，内含 1000 日元的日本星巴克充值。自 1 月 20 日起，将于日本星巴克指定店铺及 BEAMS 原宿店和官网发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100700fReUgIQ76pB3oN2H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701171007110KhAM1wolYPDO4rF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100711SiYBbqEVFA8uaymQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100712q2Hz0xYhA18KGsnu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100720ONXlQgsy0Ju42kKP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100720pOl1zn9faQXx5y4Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100725Z0qwDpFnLe5jQg3N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100956QbjmduSrRZ0VlAt8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100956NYdaLEkZKgCuFb0H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>藤原浩新的概念店 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/the-park-ing-ginza-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">THE PARK · ING GINZA，发布 2017 春季首波新品</a>。该系列以春季的野餐布花纹为主题，除了连帽衫和 T-shirt，该系列还包括  iPhone Cases、Totebag 及不同尺寸的 Pouches 及扣针。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100845HpkNGcjLIf1mTZ8M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701171008457ieGZknV9DzmK0Bs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100845BpKIx5Nvl6k3gSnD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100859tUV9Hm4FwPyaAQvp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666282\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100859DZf1owl7qnQxEHNa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100859MrCJxbHsnDSfAtp2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100859hLdT2H7fIqxgzUoy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100859jobely69Uvwr7sih.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665485\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701171008598j60cCNXiOBRUsrv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100924e08vcm7l3LrA5oRu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100924X4yRVHjcovEfWiAb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100924YK0mvsTxRw6UfdE5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100932KHmrf96BO4zTUuJ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>周杰伦任创意总监的台湾品牌 PHANTACi ，在 2016 年一整年都在做十周年企划。现今，它的十周年企划终于迎来了最后一波——与日本买手店 United Arrows 旗下品牌支线 monkey time 携手带来联名企划<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/phantaci-x-monkey-time-mr-fantastic\" rel=\"nofollow\">「Mr. FANTASTIC」系列</a>。该系列以“世界的旅人”为主题，选用了 oversize 的日本和服做样式，并加入了传统日本家徽等细节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100741O3bR2o4FgHe71lxW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100742fIAYLVQpON1RJdZz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100741WzChMwDba7FPSJjr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100751x2SkwiEfeuXAjM1n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100751LkunBq0vjYQC9wzD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100800f2wKi6RLptJXqTH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117100800Z2oIyflNHjFMvc1m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">在米兰时装周上，为了迎合 Prada 的 1970 年代主题，<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/oma-prada-milan-fashion-week-continuous-interior-fall-winter-01-16-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OMA 大都会建筑事务所，给 Prada 设计了一个像家一样的秀场</a>，观众们可以坐在“床”上看秀。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117102723OwyDA6xm0RVhEI18.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117102723q8bQKYLyh36O4PpN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117102730SikqjvBO4L31P2Kt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117102736Lv72HV4mGq9Z8yfi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117102736SXsnlAR3HidaWfzy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/a-bathing-ape-x-neighborhood-2017-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">A Bathing Ape 与 Neighborhood 的联名系列完整公开</a>。以蓝色为主调，双方共带来了 N-2B、丹宁裤、卫衣、风衣等单品，另有 BAMFORD 炮制的两款特别版 Roelx 的 Daytona 及 Submariner，该系列将于 1 月 21 日正式发售。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101004tKUuo4JfcYSAz086.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101016M5j3tDw47Cy1EGp9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101016qhyw4dmtBHNrGIaL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101024YE8D5gKAXyu9kqSd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101024NeJASZI7jGoPpWF8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101032evIfDQJME6YLxZ7S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101039vIlcoKOqRhxBsw3M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101039aGruPIjJ3bevAZpR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101039AcJZlUCRXIjpY3F4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701171010469KvX2j10bdCsSLzp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701171010459F5WqnHtE8ITvpKJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101046FOU9aEubxhscQGI7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701171010462dPE3r1LnBgmsb8e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701171010465nuKCgbRj1kANVGM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170117101056qXmEPi6sgLWO9KaS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/phantaci-x-monkey-time-mr-fantastic\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}